name: Politicians
description: Politicians, 2019, Drawing on Ps, 1034*1034 px The work consist of two paint which are "Fuck" by Trump's and Putin's mouth another one is "You" by Merkel's mouth. The persons drawn are symbolically drawn as they are well-known persons of the world who remind the word "politician". The main focus is not on the people drawn, but on the laws, orders and policies created by the states.
